   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,444:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.8 Scalability
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,445:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Scalability for mobile apps is primarily a 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,445:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: backend concern
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,446:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , but the mobile app architecture influences scalable
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,446:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: behavior:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,447:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Dimension | Mobile App Responsibility |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,447:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,448:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-----------|--------------------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,448:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,449:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,449:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: User Base Growth
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,452:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | App should not
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,453:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: assume backend topology. Use API versioning and feature flags for progressive rollout. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,453:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,453:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,454:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Data Volume
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,457:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,457:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Implement pagination (cursor-based preferred). Avoid loading unbounded data sets. Cache with eviction policies. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,458:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,458:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,459:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Concurrent Operations
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,460:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Use background processing for uploads/downloads. Don
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,460:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,461:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t block the main thread with
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,462:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: synchronous network calls. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,463:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,464:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,464:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Multi-Tenancy
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,467:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | If the app serves multiple GC departments, ensure tenant isolation in
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,468:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: local storage, configuration, and API routing. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,468:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,468:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,469:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Push Notifications
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,472:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Use APNs (iOS) and FCM (Android) or a
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,473:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: unified service. Design for notification at scale without thundering herd on backend. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,474:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,474:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,475:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Release Scalability
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,479:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,480:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Automated CI/CD pipelines with staged rollouts (1% → 10% → 50% → 100%). Feature flags for server-driven capability
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,481:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: exposure. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,482:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.9 Accessibility (WCAG / GC Standard on Accessible ICT)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,482:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: GC applications should comply with 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,483:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: WCAG 2.1 AA
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,483:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and the 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,484:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: GC Standard on Accessible ICT
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,484:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,485:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Requirement | Native iOS | Native Android | React Native |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,486:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,486:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-------------|-----------|---------------|--------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,487:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,489:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Screen
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,490:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: reader support | VoiceOver (built-in) | TalkBack (built-in) | AccessibilityInfo + native mapping |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,491:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,493:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Dynamic type /
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,494:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: font scaling | Full support | Full support | Partial (requires explicit implementation) |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,495:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,497:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Color contrast | Xcode
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,498:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Accessibility Inspector | Android Accessibility Scanner | Manual verification |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,498:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,501:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Keyboard / switch control | Full
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,502:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: platform support | Full platform support | Inconsistent across custom components |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,503:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,506:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Automated accessibility testing |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,507:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: XCUITest + accessibility audits | Espresso + AccessibilityChecks | Limited automated tooling |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,507:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: React Native caveat:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,508:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Custom components (non-native) require explicit accessibility props (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,509:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: accessible
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,510:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,512:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: accessibilityLabel
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,513:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,514:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: accessibilityRole
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,515:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ). Native platform components have accessibility built in.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.10 Localization (Official Languages)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: All GC applications should support 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,517:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: English and French
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,518:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  as per the Official Languages Act.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,518:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Concern | Practice |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,520:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,520:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---------|----------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,521:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,521:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,522:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: String Externalization
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,523:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | All user-facing strings should be in localization
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,524:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: files (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,524:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .strings
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,525:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: /
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,526:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .stringsdict
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,526:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  on iOS, 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,527:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: strings.xml
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,528:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  on Android, i18n JSON for RN). |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,529:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,529:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,530:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Layout
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,531:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Flexibility
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,533:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | French text is typically 15–30% longer than English. UI should accommodate variable text length without
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,533:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: truncation. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,534:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,535:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,535:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Date/Time/Number Formatting
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,536:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Use 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,537:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Locale
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,537:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: -aware formatters. Never hardcode date formats. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,538:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,539:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,540:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Accessibility + Localization
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,540:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,541:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: accessibilityLabel
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,542:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  values should also be localized. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,542:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,543:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,545:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: RTL Consideration
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,552:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,554:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: While not required for EN/FR, if the app will serve Indigenous languages or other scripts, RTL layout support
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,555:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: should be architecturally considered. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,556:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.11 Data Sovereignty and Privacy
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,557:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Requirement | Implementation |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,558:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,559:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-------------|---------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,560:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,560:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,562:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Data Residency
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,570:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | All backend services should be hosted
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,571:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: within Canada per applicable policy. API endpoints should resolve to Canadian data centers. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,572:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,573:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,574:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: On-Device Data
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,579:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,581:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Minimize data stored on device. Encrypt all local data at rest. Implement remote wipe capability (via MDM or
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,583:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: app-level). |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,584:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,584:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,585:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Privacy Impact Assessment
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,587:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Required before deployment. Mobile-specific considerations: device
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,588:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: telemetry, location data, biometric data processing. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,588:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,589:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,589:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Data Minimization
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,591:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Collect only what is necessary. Do not
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,591:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cache sensitive data beyond session requirements. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,592:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,593:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,593:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Consent
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,598:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | If collecting analytics or telemetry beyond essential
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,600:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: functionality, user consent should be obtained with clear bilingual explanation. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,601:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.12 Configuration Management
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,602:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Concern | Practice |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,603:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,604:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---------|----------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,604:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,605:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,606:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: No Hardcoded Secrets
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | API keys, client IDs, endpoints — none should be
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,610:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: hardcoded in the binary. Use build-time injection or remote configuration. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,610:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,611:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,613:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Environment Separation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,616:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Dev,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,617:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Staging, Production configurations should be isolated. Build variants / schemes for each. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,617:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,618:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,618:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Remote Configuration
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,622:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,624:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Feature flags and non-sensitive configuration can be fetched from a secure remote config service. Cached locally
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with TTL. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,625:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,626:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,626:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Build Reproducibility
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,629:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Builds should be reproducible from source for audit. Pin all dependency
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,630:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: versions. Use lockfiles. |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,630:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 6.13 Dependency and Supply-Chain Security
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,631:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Concern | Native iOS/Android | React Native |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,632:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,632:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |---------|-------------------|--------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,633:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,633:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,634:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Package Ecosystem
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,638:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,639:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: CocoaPods/SPM (iOS), Maven/Gradle (Android) — smaller, curated | npm — massive, higher risk of typosquatting and
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: malicious packages |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,641:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,641:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,642:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Dependency Count
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,644:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Typically 10–30 direct dependencies | Typically 30–100+ direct dependencies
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,645:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (each with transitive deps) |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,645:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,646:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,647:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: SBOM Generation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,648:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Standard tooling available | Standard tooling available
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,649:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (CycloneDX, SPDX) |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,649:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,650:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,650:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Vulnerability Scanning
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,651:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Dependabot, Snyk | Dependabot, Snyk, 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,652:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: npm audit
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,652:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,653:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,653:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,654:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Lock
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,654:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Files
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,655:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,656:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Podfile.lock
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,656:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , Gradle dependency locking | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,657:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: package-lock.json
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,657:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  / 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,658:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: yarn.lock
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,658:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — must be committed |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,659:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,660:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,661:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,662:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Integrity Verification
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,663:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Package signatures (SPM, Maven Central) | npm package provenance (partial adoption) |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,663:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Recommendation:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,664:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  For GC applications, maintain a 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,665:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: curated allow-list
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,668:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  of approved dependencies. Conduct security
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,669:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: review of any new dependency before inclusion. Automate vulnerability scanning in CI/CD.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,670:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 7. Security Controls Comparison — Native vs. React Native vs. WebView
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,671:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Security Control | Native iOS (Swift) | Native Android (Kotlin) | React Native | WebView Shell |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,672:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,673:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-----------------|-------------------|------------------------|--------------|---------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,673:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,674:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,675:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Secure Enclave / StrongBox
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,679:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Direct
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,681:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: API | ✅ Direct API | ⚠️ Native module required | ❌ Not accessible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,682:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,683:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
