   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,684:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,685:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: URLSession
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,687:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  delegate | ✅ Network
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,688:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Security Config + OkHttp | ⚠️ Native module | ❌ Not feasible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,689:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,689:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,690:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: App Attestation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,694:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ App Attest (DeviceCheck) | ✅ Play
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,697:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Integrity API | ⚠️ Native module | ❌ Not possible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,698:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,700:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,702:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Jailbreak / Root Detection
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,706:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Native checks | ✅ SafetyNet / Play Integrity |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,707:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ⚠️ Native module | ❌ Not possible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,708:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,709:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,710:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Code Obfuscation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,715:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Compiled binary; symbols strippable | ✅ ProGuard / R8 | ⚠️ Hermes
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,716:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: bytecode (less effective) | ❌ Plain JavaScript |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,717:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,717:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,718:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Anti-Tampering
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,730:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Code signing verification at OS level | ✅ APK signature
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,734:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: verification | ⚠️ Code signing applies to native shell only; JS bundle can be modified on jailbroken devices | ❌ No local
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,735:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: integrity |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,736:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,737:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,738:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Biometric Gate for Keys
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,741:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,743:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: SecAccessControl
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,744:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  with biometry | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,745:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: setUserAuthenticationRequired
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,746:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ⚠️ Via native module bridge | ❌ Not available |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,747:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,748:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,749:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Secure IPC
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,754:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ App Groups
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,755:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with encryption | ✅ Content Providers with permissions | ⚠️ Depends on implementation | ❌ Not applicable |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,756:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,757:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,758:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Screenshot /
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,761:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Screen Recording Prevention
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,763:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,766:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: UITextField.isSecureTextEntry
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,768:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , scene delegate | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,769:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: FLAG_SECURE
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,771:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ⚠️
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,772:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Native module | ❌ Not possible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,773:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,774:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,775:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Clipboard Protection
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,776:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,776:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: UIPasteboard
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,777:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  with expiration (iOS 16+) | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,778:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ClipboardManager
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,779:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  with flags | ⚠️ Native module | ❌ Web clipboard API only |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,781:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,782:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,785:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Debugger Detection
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,787:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,788:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: sysctl
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,788:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  / 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,789:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ptrace
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,790:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  checks | ✅ Debug.isDebuggerConnected() | ⚠️ Native module | ❌ Not possible |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,793:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,796:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,798:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Runtime Integrity
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,805:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Binary is
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,807:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: verified by OS on every launch | ✅ APK integrity on install | ⚠️ JS bundle integrity must be manually verified | ❌ No runtime
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,809:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: integrity |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,810:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,811:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,813:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Network Traffic Inspection Resistance
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,817:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Custom URLProtocol + pinning | ✅ Custom TrustManager +
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,819:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pinning | ⚠️ Achievable with native modules | ❌ System proxy is used |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,823:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Key Insight:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,826:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  React Native can achieve 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,827:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: most
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,831:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  of the security controls available to native platforms, but every
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,833:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: security-critical capability requires a native module bridge. This means:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,833:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,835:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The development team must have 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,837:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: native iOS and Android expertise
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,839:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  in addition to React Native
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,840:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: skills
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,841:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,842:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Each security feature is a 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,843:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: custom integration
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,845:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  rather than a platform-provided capability
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,849:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,852:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The security surface area is 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,853:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: larger
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,856:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  because both the JS layer and the native bridge must be secured
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,857:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: If the team does not have native mobile expertise, React Native
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,859:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s security posture will be significantly weaker than a
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,860:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: native implementation.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,861:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 8. Decision Tree — Selecting the Right Architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,862:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: START: What is the data classification?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,862:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,863:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ├─── Protected B or higher
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,864:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,865:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    ├─── Do you have native iOS + Android developers?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,866:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    ├── YES → Native iOS (Swift) + Native Android (Kotlin)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,867:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │         [Maximum security controls, direct HSM access,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,867:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │          app attestation, no JS bridge attack surface]
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,868:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,868:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    └── NO → React Native with mandatory native security modules
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,869:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │              [Custom native modules for: HSM key management,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,870:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │               DPoP proof generation, mTLS, app attestation,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,871:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │               jailbreak detection. Requires native expertise
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,872:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │               for security-critical components.]
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,872:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,874:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    └─── ⚠️ WebView Shell presents elevated risk — requires documented risk
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,955:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: acceptance
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,956:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,957:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ├─── Protected A
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,957:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,958:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    ├─── Is offline capability critical?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,959:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    ├── YES → React Native or Native
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,959:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │         [Local data storage with encryption, background
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,961:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │          sync, offline-first architecture]
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,962:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,963:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    └── NO → React Native (generally cost-efficient)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,964:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │              [Standard OIDC + PKCE + DPoP, Keychain/Keystore
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,964:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │               via react-native-keychain]
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,965:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,966:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    └─── ⚠️ WebView Shell presents elevated risk — requires documented risk
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,967:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: acceptance
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,967:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,968:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ├─── Unclassified (Public-facing informational app)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,968:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,969:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    ├─── Does the app require authentication?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,971:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    ├── YES → React Native with standard OIDC + PKCE
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,973:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │    └── NO  → React Native or Progressive Web App (PWA)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,975:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,977:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │    └─── WebView hybrid MAY be acceptable (with informed risk
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,979:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: acceptance)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,981:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,982:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: └─── Questions to ask for any path:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,983:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,984:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      ├── Q1: What is the user base size? (hundreds vs. millions)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,985:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → Influences backend scalability and push notification
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,987:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,988:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,988:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      ├── Q2: What devices are supported? (GC-managed only vs. BYOD)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,989:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → Managed devices enable mTLS via MDM-provisioned certificates
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,990:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → BYOD requires alternative device attestation (App Attest /
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,991:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Play Integrity)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,991:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,992:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      ├── Q3: What is the expected offline duration?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,992:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → Extended offline needs local encrypted database + sync
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,993:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: strategy
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,994:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,996:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      ├── Q4: What is the maintenance budget?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,997:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → Two native codebases = ~2x maintenance; RN = ~1.3x vs single
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,998:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: web app
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:31,999:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,000:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      ├── Q5: Are there existing native development teams?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,001:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │   → Leveraging existing capability reduces risk and ramp-up time
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,001:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      │
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,002:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:      └── Q6: What is the deployment model?
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,003:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:          → Public app stores vs. enterprise MDM distribution vs. both
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,003:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Decision Summary Table
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,004:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Scenario | Recommended Platform | Rationale |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,005:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,006:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |----------|---------------------|-----------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,006:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,011:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | High-assurance, Protected B,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,013:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: managed devices | Native iOS + Native Android | Maximum security controls, direct HSM, app attestation |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,014:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,018:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,020:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: High-assurance, Protected B, BYOD | Native or React Native + native security modules | Device attestation replaces
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,021:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: MDM-provisioned certs |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,021:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,023:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Standard internal app, Protected A | React Native | Cost-efficient; security achievable
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,024:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with native modules |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,024:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,025:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Public-facing informational | React Native or PWA | Widest reach; minimal security
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,026:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: requirements |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,027:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,030:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Field app with extended offline | Native (preferred) or React Native | Complex sync + crypto
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,030:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: operations benefit from native perf |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,031:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,032:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | App requiring frequent iteration | React Native | Faster development cycle;
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,033:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: shared codebase |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,034:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9. Security Incident Event (SIE) Response — Architecture for Rapid
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,035:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Containment
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: A critical factor in mobile architecture selection is the ability to 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: detect, contain, and remediate security incidents
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,038:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,039:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: with maximum speed and control. The following outlines how Microsoft
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,039:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,040:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s current technology stack enables SIE
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: response across mobile architectures.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,042:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9.1 SIE Response Capabilities by Architecture
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Capability | Native (Swift/Kotlin) | React Native | WebView Shell |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-----------|----------------------|--------------|---------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,045:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,045:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,046:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Remote session revocation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,051:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Immediate via token
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,052:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: revocation + Conditional Access | ✅ Immediate via token revocation + Conditional Access | ✅ Immediate via session
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,053:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: invalidation |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,054:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,054:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,055:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Remote device wipe
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,056:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Via Microsoft Intune MDM | ✅ Via Microsoft Intune MDM | ⚠️ Partial — web session
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,057:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: only |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,057:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,058:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,059:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Selective app data wipe
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,060:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | ✅ Intune App Protection Policies (APP) | ✅ Intune APP with RN wrapper | ❌ Limited —
   DEBUG: 2026-04-13 14:51:32,061:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: browser cache only |
